{"tid":1206883,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"長遠黎講我覺得需要建立一個係現場非電子嘅溝通系統","createTime":"2019-06-12T04:23:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T02:25:48.000Z","uid":24691,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"87d53356d341a4eb9ea1047982c7c7becfc56186","tid":1206883,"uid":24691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T04:23:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YofgroB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYofgroB.png&h=2ca31363&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見到有人話用白板<br />\n用白板係好但係距離遠少少都睇唔到寫乜<br />\n我覺得肢體語言加顏色然之後整條list 出黎可能有得諗<br />\n不如大家比下意見？"},{"pid":"989619215615766d9b2e0dae0d3d5606b83a1f6b","tid":1206883,"uid":61398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T04:31:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1601dc758d2c261d023d5dbd8cf8db7d2db60f73","tid":1206883,"uid":24691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T04:40:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb95e2d84d08a6a79731f91b01d92cc4c0c7440b","tid":1206883,"uid":249885,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T05:05:31.000Z","msg":"你不如用顏色煙仲好 eg 黑=危險 黃=增援 紅=衝"},{"pid":"1c25089c48abf9d134e676ee44039f0fcdfca84a","tid":1206883,"uid":24691,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"eb95e2d84d08a6a79731f91b01d92cc4c0c7440b","tid":1206883,"uid":249885,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T05:05:31.000Z","msg":"你不如用顏色煙仲好 eg 黑=危險 黃=增援 紅=衝"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:50:42.000Z","msg":"邊撚度黎煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你燒野放煙咪仲on9"},{"pid":"97bcc32fd4bac828e057b7f0fa27bbb915470027","tid":1206883,"uid":57698,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"eb95e2d84d08a6a79731f91b01d92cc4c0c7440b","tid":1206883,"uid":249885,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T05:05:31.000Z","msg":"你不如用顏色煙仲好 eg 黑=危險 黃=增援 紅=衝"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:52:30.000Z","msg":"放煙好似玩